  "text": "Google News has quickly become the preferred method to conduct news-based content analyses since its inception in 2002 (Carlson, 2007) . The method has already been used by researchers to conduct news-based content analyses on a variety of subjects including TASER ® lawsuits (Adams & Jennison, 2007) , human trafficking [CITATION_1] , shaken baby syndrome [CITATION_2] , medical research funding [CITATION_3] ; and, influenza infections among children [CITATION_4] . ",
